47
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,400
You certainly criticized it.

48
00:01:56,150 --> 00:01:56,640
You said...

49
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:59,230
You... What was it again?

50
00:01:59,510 --> 00:02:00,040
What?

51
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,400
Extremely poor taste!

52
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,230
Sycophantic flattery!

53
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:06,790
Nonsense from start to end!

54
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:10,910
Accurate!

55
00:02:11,870 --> 00:02:13,150
Particularly accurate!

56
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,960
I've shown it to so many people.

57
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,240
None dared tell me this!

58
00:02:17,910 --> 00:02:18,750
Only Professor Ding is

59
00:02:19,870 --> 00:02:20,910
upright and unyielding!

60
00:02:21,870 --> 00:02:22,520
I toast to you!

61
00:02:22,910 --> 00:02:23,280
Here!

62
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:25,840
No, I can't.

63
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:27,430
No more, please.

64
00:02:27,430 --> 00:02:28,520
Just one more!

65
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:29,190
I...

66
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,910
I really can't drink anymore.

67
00:02:32,870 --> 00:02:33,870
No, I can't.

68
00:02:39,590 --> 00:02:40,360
Zhiyuan.

69
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:44,150
Mr. Li's told me many times.

70
00:02:44,750 --> 00:02:47,280
You're his most respected figure

71
00:02:47,710 --> 00:02:49,080
in the cultural circle.

72
00:02:49,150 --> 00:02:49,710
Yes!

73
00:02:49,710 --> 00:02:52,000
He'll be heartbroken if you don't drink.

74
00:02:52,190 --> 00:02:52,710
No, I can't.

75
00:02:52,710 --> 00:02:53,310
How about this?

76
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:56,150
You drink half, and I drink half, okay?

77
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:58,030
No, no.

78
00:02:58,910 --> 00:03:01,190
That absolutely won't do!

79
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:03,710
Professor Ding, a real man

80
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:05,310
can't let a woman take the drink for him.

81
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:08,280
You should cherish the fairer sex!

82
00:03:12,190 --> 00:03:12,840
Last cup.

83
00:03:12,910 --> 00:03:13,310
Last cup.

84
00:03:14,910 --> 00:03:15,470
Last cup.

85
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:15,750
Here.

86
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:17,630
Here.

87
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:18,400
Here, pour me some.

88
00:03:18,470 --> 00:03:19,120
There you go.

89
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:23,080
Here!

90
00:03:24,310 --> 00:03:25,080
Straight from the pot!

91
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:26,280
Last cup.

92
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:26,960
I respect you!

93
00:03:32,150 --> 00:03:33,560
Alright, we're done.

94
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,000
No more drinking.

95
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:38,840
Drink some water.

96
00:03:39,470 --> 00:03:39,910
Some water.

97
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,400
Professor Ding.

98
00:03:46,470 --> 00:03:47,080
I

99
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:50,400
wanted you to write the preface,
but you've been busy.

100
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:52,280
So I had someone else write it instead.

101
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:53,310
Take a look at this.

102
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:55,030
If you find it alright,

103
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:57,150
sign here, and it's as good as yours.

104
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,910
Saves trouble, doesn't it?

105
00:03:59,080 --> 00:04:00,400
Here.

106
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:01,120
Take a look.

107
00:04:02,910 --> 00:04:04,960
Here we go again. My signature?

108
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,590
Look. It's just a signature.

109
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:07,800
I won't sign.

110
00:04:09,630 --> 00:04:11,470
See? They've already written it.

111
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:13,470
Just have a look.

112
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,000
Just take a look.

113
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:17,510
Look, it's quite good.

114
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:33,480
Why sign if I didn't write it?

115
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:41,630
Forget it, forget it.

116
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:43,120
Seriously, I'm done.

117
00:04:43,390 --> 00:04:45,120
Such fuss over one signature.

118
00:04:45,270 --> 00:04:47,070
I know he despises me. I quit!

119
00:04:47,420 --> 00:04:48,060
Oh my.

120
00:04:49,390 --> 00:04:50,190
Mr. Li

121
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:53,360
Don't say that.

122
00:04:53,660 --> 00:04:54,500
No, forget it.

123
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,190
The thing is, Zhiyuan,

124
00:04:56,190 --> 00:04:58,830
-I didn't write it.
-he treasures his reputation.

125
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:00,240
If you use a ghostwriter,

126
00:05:00,310 --> 00:05:02,800
he needs to review before signing it.

127
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:03,510
I'm done with this!

128
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:07,780
Zhiyuan.

129
00:05:07,780 --> 00:05:08,420
Ah.

130
00:05:09,950 --> 00:05:10,560
I...

131
00:05:10,700 --> 00:05:11,260
Uh?

132
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,240
I've reviewed it.

133
00:05:12,870 --> 00:05:13,800
It's passable.

134
00:05:14,750 --> 00:05:16,000
When you have time later,

135
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:17,700
just give some more feedback.

136
00:05:17,700 --> 00:05:18,220
Hm.

137
00:05:18,390 --> 00:05:20,120
It just needs slight modifications.

138
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:20,750
Modifications?

139
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,000
For today though,

140
00:05:22,630 --> 00:05:23,600
just sign here.

141
00:05:24,310 --> 00:05:26,160
The publisher is in a hurry.

142
00:05:26,390 --> 00:05:27,360
When the revisions are made,

143
00:05:27,830 --> 00:05:29,190
they'll definitely let you review again.

144
00:05:29,630 --> 00:05:30,600
Right, Mr. Li?

145
00:05:30,660 --> 00:05:30,950
Yes!

146
00:05:30,950 --> 00:05:31,480
Right?

147
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:32,630
Yes, good.

148
00:05:32,830 --> 00:05:34,190
Come on, let's sign.

149
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:35,830
Here.

150
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:36,750
Sign?

151
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,560
Over here.

152
00:05:39,190 --> 00:05:39,510
Come.

153
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,310
Here, right here.

154
00:05:44,870 --> 00:05:45,830
Not there.

155
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:46,720
The back.

156
00:05:49,430 --> 00:05:49,870
Here.

157
00:05:50,190 --> 00:05:50,800
Yes.

158
00:05:51,830 --> 00:05:52,160
Here.

159
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,120
There you go.

160
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,430
Done.

161
00:06:01,020 --> 00:06:02,260
[Ding Zhiyuan]

162
00:06:10,190 --> 00:06:10,680
Signed.

163
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:11,430
All done.

164
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:12,950
Are you alright?

165
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:15,800
Quick!

166
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,480
You okay?

167
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,160
Go on, there!

168
00:06:20,510 --> 00:06:21,310
Are you okay?

169
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,950
So much effort for a signature.

170
00:06:25,950 --> 00:06:27,510
Look at this, he even threw up.

171
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:33,480
Linjiang.

172
00:06:35,190 --> 00:06:35,560
Dad.

173
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,430
What I want to tell you is,

174
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:43,680
back then, because I was too ambitious,

175
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,240
I chose your mom.

176
00:06:46,630 --> 00:06:47,800
But all these years

177
00:06:48,430 --> 00:06:51,360
I've only felt guilty toward Ma Xiaowei.

178
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:55,040
I've never done

179
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,830
anything to betray your mom.

180
00:06:59,070 --> 00:06:59,800
Trust me.

181
00:07:08,310 --> 00:07:09,950
Dad, don't talk about this.

182
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:12,160
When you were in the ICU,

183
00:07:12,830 --> 00:07:13,920
I already figured it out.

184
00:07:14,870 --> 00:07:16,070
What happened doesn't matter.

185
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,190
Only your health matters.

186
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:22,950
Let bygones be bygones.

187
00:07:24,310 --> 00:07:24,720
Your meds.

188
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,120
Come in.

189
00:07:30,310 --> 00:07:32,360
Mr. Ai, it's us.

190
00:07:33,070 --> 00:07:35,310
You can sit up already? That's great.

191
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:36,510
Let me take my medicine.

192
00:07:36,950 --> 00:07:37,830
Take it easy.

193
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,360
Thank you for visiting me.

194
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,720
We're relieved you're okay.

195
00:07:48,270 --> 00:07:50,160
Chen told me what you did

196
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,270
during my coma these days.

197
00:07:53,270 --> 00:07:54,600
I really appreciate your help.

198
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:57,160
And you too, young man.

199
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,430
I should thank you as well.

200
00:07:58,950 --> 00:07:59,430
My pleasure.

201
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,600
Don't dwell on it, it's all over now.

202
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:03,800
Focus on recovering.

203
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,600
Surviving disaster brings blessings.

204
00:08:06,310 --> 00:08:07,480
Blessings?

205
00:08:08,870 --> 00:08:10,510
Blessings my foot!

206
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:14,800
Even my own son wanted me dead.

207
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,240
Where are those blessings?

208
00:08:16,870 --> 00:08:19,800
How can people be so vicious?

209
00:08:20,390 --> 00:08:21,920
Dad, stop thinking about this.

210
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,160
I'll handle his situation.

211
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:24,920
Dad! Dad!

212
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:25,830
Dad!

213
00:08:25,830 --> 00:08:26,240
Why are you here?

214
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,000
I came to see my dad!

215
00:08:27,190 --> 00:08:27,950
Dad! Step aside!

216
00:08:28,070 --> 00:08:28,510
You can't go in!

217
00:08:28,510 --> 00:08:28,950
Why are you here?

218
00:08:28,950 --> 00:08:29,630
Stop! This is a hospital.

219
00:08:29,630 --> 00:08:30,430
- I came to... - Get out!

220
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:31,270
Let me apologize to Dad!

221
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:31,680
Dad!

222
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:32,080
No need.

223
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,630
What I did was too extreme!

224
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,790
I had no choice, Dad!

225
00:08:34,790 --> 00:08:35,510
Please listen to me!

226
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:37,200
Dad, are you abandoning me? Dad!

227
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:38,080
- Stop shouting. - Dad!

228
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,200
Linjiang... Linjiang.

229
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:40,440
Dad...

230
00:08:40,670 --> 00:08:41,390
Let him in.

231
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:44,670
Dad...

232
00:08:46,670 --> 00:08:47,120
Are you okay?

233
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:48,440
Dad...

234
00:08:49,550 --> 00:08:50,000
Dad...

235
00:08:50,630 --> 00:08:51,960
I was wrong, Dad.

236
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,960
It was all my so-called friends

237
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:56,080
who gave me the idea.

238
00:08:56,270 --> 00:08:57,720
I saw you unconscious then.

239
00:08:58,000 --> 00:09:00,080
I was... I was panicking.

240
00:09:00,390 --> 00:09:01,150
I just... I just...

241
00:09:01,270 --> 00:09:02,910
You wanted me dead, didn't you?

242
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:03,790
No!

243
00:09:04,030 --> 00:09:06,600
Dad, I'm sorry.

244
00:09:06,870 --> 00:09:07,790
Dad, I'm a bastard!

245
00:09:07,870 --> 00:09:09,440
I'm sorry! I'm an animal!

246
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:11,440
Please forgive me, Dad.

247
00:09:12,030 --> 00:09:13,790
Okay, stop hitting yourself.

248
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:16,120
You should leave now, go.

249
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:17,390
Dad...

250
00:09:17,870 --> 00:09:18,200
Dad...

251
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,440
I'm terrified of poverty, Dad.

252
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:21,790
We were truly destitute.

253
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:24,320
Mom cut ties with her family long ago.

254
00:09:24,910 --> 00:09:27,240
She worked any job she could find

255
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:29,240
just to raise me, Dad.

256
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:31,600
Dad, it's true!

257
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:34,080
Ma Xiaowei, stop playing the victim.

258
00:09:34,630 --> 00:09:35,480
If your mother knew

259
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,600
you could do something like this,

260
00:09:36,910 --> 00:09:38,270
she'd regret ever giving birth to you,

261
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:39,390
Alright.

262
00:09:40,270 --> 00:09:41,960
Xiaowei, you should leave now.

263
00:09:42,790 --> 00:09:44,030
If anything comes up later,

264
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,480
Chen will handle it.

265
00:09:46,910 --> 00:09:47,440
Go.

266
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:48,720
Go.

267
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,000
Dad... Dad...

268
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:51,240
Look.

269
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:53,240
Mom kept

270
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:56,030
this photo under the pillow.

271
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,630
Look at it, just look.

272
00:09:59,390 --> 00:10:00,270
If Mom knew

273
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:02,960
you wouldn't take care of me,

274
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:05,270
she'd die with regrets, Dad!

275
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,320
Dad!

276
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:10,390
Mom!

277
00:10:12,030 --> 00:10:12,840
Mom!

278
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,510
Mom!

279
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:18,240
Why did you even give birth to me?

280
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:21,510
Why didn't you take me with you
when you left?

281
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,360
Why did you

282
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:26,320
leave me to suffer in this world?

283
00:10:26,550 --> 00:10:27,240
Mom!

284
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,120
Why?

285
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:31,840
Enough!

286
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:33,030
Mom, why?

287
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:35,240
Just leave now, okay?

288
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,080
Go.

289
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,600
Mom!

290
00:10:38,550 --> 00:10:40,120
Go!

291
00:10:40,910 --> 00:10:41,630
That's enough!

292
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:45,120
We'll talk again

293
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,120
about what to do.

294
00:10:58,150 --> 00:11:00,790
Okay, we'll talk later.

295
00:11:01,030 --> 00:11:01,960
Dad, you take care.

296
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,390
