721
00:32:26,480 --> 00:32:28,790
Many people want to team up with me.

722
00:32:29,480 --> 00:32:30,720
I know, I know.

723
00:32:31,030 --> 00:32:31,830
Because you're

724
00:32:31,830 --> 00:32:33,400
