Elaborate.

726
00:32:39,400 --> 00:32:39,750
Come on.

727
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:41,400
Expand on that.

728
00:32:45,310 --> 00:32:46,030
You see,

729
00:32:47,270 --> 00:32:49,110
I've actually learned

730
00:32:50,000 --> 00:32:51,070
